    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\tToday\u2019s Climate: Biden\u2019s New Highway Rule Offers Some Hope for His Faltering Climate Agenda\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\tBy Kristoffer Tigue\n\n\t\t\n\t",
      "url": "https://insideclimatenews.org/todaysclimate/bidens-new-highway-rule-offers-some-hope-for-his-faltering-climate-agenda/"
